A: You just have not implemented partition in its entirety.
It should probably look like this:
int p = partition(nums, low, high);
while (p == low) {
  if (++p >= high) { break; } // nothing to the right of the pivot
}
while (p == high) {
  if (--p <= low) { break; } // nothing to the left of the pivot
}
quicksort(nums, low, p - 1);
quicksort(nums, p + 1, high);

You probably want to also call quicksort when there are only 2 items left for each partition call.

